
'''安大略省服务处'''<ref>{{Cite web|title=省府提醒省民 過期證照現需更新|url=http://www.mingpaocanada.com/TOR/htm/NEWS/20210902/tde1_r.htm|access-date=2022-03-22|work=www.mingpaocanada.com|publisher=明報加拿大}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=日後仍需更新車牌貼紙 確保有汽車保險及追討罰款|url=http://www.mingpaocanada.com/TOR/htm/NEWS/20220223/taa2_r.htm|access-date=2022-03-22|work=www.mingpaocanada.com|publisher=明報加拿大|archive-date=2022-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220225043541/http://www.mingpaocanada.com/TOR/htm/News/20220223/taa2_r.htm}}</ref>（{{lang-en|'''ServiceOntario'''}}，中文简称'''安省服务处'''）指[[加拿大|加拿大]][[安大略省政府|安大略省政府]]政府及消费者服务厅下辖的各个办事处，负责在[[安大略省|全省]]范围内提供点对点的省政府服务。安省服务处成立于2006年，其主要通过网络或面对面的服务站点提供服务，同时也运营电话呼叫中心。<ref name="ag report 13">{{cite report |author=Auditor General of Ontario |date=2013 |title=Annual Report of the Office of the Auditor General of Ontario: Ministry of Government Services |url=https://www.auditor.on.ca/en/content/annualreports/arreports/en13/309en13.pdf |publisher=Queen's Printer for Ontario |access-date=20 May 2020 |archive-date=2020-09-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200927123305/https://www.auditor.on.ca/en/content/annualreports/arreports/en13/309en13.pdf }}</ref>

该处的一些服务曾经由布置在各主要购物中心的自助服务亭提供<ref name="ag report 13">{{cite report |author=Auditor General of Ontario |date= 2013 |title=Annual Report of the Office of the Auditor General of Ontario: Ministry of Government Services |url=https://www.auditor.on.ca/en/content/annualreports/arreports/en13/309en13.pdf |publisher=Queen's Printer for Ontario |access-date= 20 May 2020}}</ref>；但在2012年，[[大多伦多地区|大多伦多地区]]的部分服务亭被发现安装了非法卡片扫描装置，造成全省自助服务亭系统因安全原因而关闭<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.680news.com/news/local/article/370648--serviceontario-kiosks-remain-out-of-order-after-illegal-card-readers-found |title=ServiceOntario kiosks remain out of order after illegal card readers found |publisher=680News |access-date=12 June 2012}}</ref>。一年以后安省政府宣布服务亭系统永久关闭<ref>{{cite news |author1=Government of Ontario |title=ServiceOntario kiosks permanently closed |url=https://news.ontario.ca/mgs/en/2012/11/serviceontario-kiosks-permanently-closed.html |accessdate=2017-06-14 |archive-date=2019-02-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190214021604/https://news.ontario.ca/mgs/en/2012/11/serviceontario-kiosks-permanently-closed.html }}</ref>。

